WEBVTT

00:03.445 --> 00:06.421
Happy first day of school breakfast!

00:06.466 --> 00:09.891
This year's theme... Second. Guess why?

00:09.930 --> 00:12.648
Because the theme is always just
whatever grade I'm starting?

00:12.688 --> 00:14.557
Not true. Pre-school was "Bunnies."

00:14.604 --> 00:15.725
Now, sit.

00:15.758 --> 00:17.860
This year,

00:17.894 --> 00:20.731
we're having Stackie Robinsons

00:20.763 --> 00:24.300
in honor of Hall of Fame
second baseman Jackie Robinson.

00:24.333 --> 00:26.774
I had a protein shake before my run.

00:26.806 --> 00:28.118
I've been up since 5:00.

00:28.143 --> 00:29.173
You went for a run?

00:29.205 --> 00:31.508
- Alone? In the dark?
- Relax.

00:31.541 --> 00:32.976
I was on the treadmill.

00:33.008 --> 00:35.244
Blacktop is murder on my knees.

00:35.300 --> 00:37.336
Yikes. Better hit the road.

00:37.402 --> 00:40.371
Hit the road to school, right?

00:40.405 --> 00:42.073
Yeah. Where else would I be going?

00:42.106 --> 00:44.643
Um, your high-powered job
in advertising?

00:45.777 --> 00:48.045
You haven't changed a bit.

00:48.079 --> 00:50.149
Yeah. Neither have you.

00:51.182 --> 00:52.651
We stopped for coffee.

00:52.683 --> 00:54.819
Sophie got a punch card.
Her next coffee's free.

00:54.853 --> 00:56.954
Then we listened to NPR
the whole ride here.

00:56.987 --> 00:58.006
It's like she went away

00:58.031 --> 00:59.423
to Lance Bass Space Camp a little girl

00:59.457 --> 01:00.893
and came back a middle-aged commuter.

01:00.926 --> 01:02.094
She reminds me of my mom.

01:02.127 --> 01:04.163
Did Graham change
at Lance Bass Space Camp?

01:04.196 --> 01:05.898
Ask him yourself.

01:05.931 --> 01:08.267
I'm a new man, W.C.

01:08.300 --> 01:09.358
Check it.

01:09.383 --> 01:11.883
- Ankle socks.
- See?

01:11.908 --> 01:13.472
Sophie wants to be an emancipated minor

01:13.505 --> 01:15.240
and Graham's got a sock thing.

01:15.273 --> 01:16.475
Change is everywhere.

01:16.508 --> 01:17.921
So true.

01:17.946 --> 01:19.645
I don't know how I'm gonna handle

01:19.678 --> 01:21.079
Jack starting pre-school.

01:22.479 --> 01:24.515
Okay. Mwah. Okay.

01:24.548 --> 01:26.651
Enjoy your first day, buddy.

01:26.684 --> 01:28.353
Make me proud.

01:28.386 --> 01:30.655
You know this school starts

01:30.688 --> 01:32.023
at kindergarten, right?

01:34.191 --> 01:35.986
Huh.

